para_trans: Held to mark the centenary year
Government Decision No: AVI-2025 / Q. No. 206/25 Ka-5
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
The year 2025 is the centenary year of the 350th Shaheedi Samagam of Sri Guru Tegh Bahadur Sahib Ji.
May their glorious history be known to the Savas, as well as their preaching and sacrifices.
To commemorate the day, various events were organised in Nagpur, Raigad and Nanded in the state.
